#Text=The Denver Nuggets ( 19 - 30 ) defeated the Toronto Raptors ( 32 - 16 ) 112 - 93 on Monday .

#Text=Despite a sterling record , impressive 11 - game winning streak and comfortable division lead coming into Monday , the Raptors did n't exactly travel well into Denver 's mile - high altitude.Toronto was held to pedestrian 37 and 32 percent tallies from the field and three - point range , respectively , while yielding 54 and 46 percent figures to Denver in those same categories .

#Text=Even more surprisingly , a Nuggets team with a multi - season reputation of struggling against opposing big men down did a complete about - face Monday , dominating the Raptors on the boards and in the paint .
#Text=They outscored the visitors by the margin of 60 - 26 down low , and outrebounded them 49 - 26 .
#Text=The charge was led by the emerging Nikola Jokic , who posted 27 points and hauled in 14 rebounds , 11 of them coming on the defensive glass .
#Text=Three other Denver players - - Kenneth Faried , Will Barton and Jusuf Nurkic - - collected seven boards apiece as well , in a game that turned into a thoroughly unexpected rout .
#Text=DeMar DeRozan was essentially the lone bright spot for Toronto , registering a team - high 24 points and adding four assists , a rebound and a steal .
#Text=Terrence Ross was actually the next biggest contributor , scoring 12 points , hauling in four rebounds and collecting a steal off the bench .
#Text=Kyle Lowry posted a modest 10 points , which he supplemented with a pair of rebounds , a pair of assists and a trio of thefts .
#Text=Jonas Valanciunas , saddled with a thumb sprain suffered on Saturday versus the Pistons , held his own against Jokic early before exiting after 19 minutes .
#Text=He amassed 10 points , eight rebounds and a block over his relatively brief time on the floor .
#Text=Despite the loss , the Raptors sit atop the Eastern Conference 's Atlantic Division .
#Text=They are in Phoenix on Tuesday night for a date with the Suns .
#Text=Jokic added four assists and a block to his game - high scoring and rebounding totals .
#Text=Barton paced the Nuggets bench with the next - highest scoring haul of the game , collecting 20 points and adding the aforementioned seven rebounds , three assists and a block .
#Text=Fellow reserve Randy Foye was right behind him with 16 points of his own , which he complemented with five rebounds , three assists , a steal and a pair of blocks .
#Text=Danilo Gallinari and Kenneth Faried followed with a pair of 13 - point efforts .
#Text=Gallinari also pitched in four rebounds , four assists and a steal , while Faried secured his seven boards and also dished out two assists and recorded a steal .
#Text=The Nuggets remain in fourth place in the Western Conference 's Northwest Division .
#Text=They head to Utah to take on the Jazz on Wednesday .
